A customer has requested the ability to review page history in a side-by-side comparison mode. A user could take any two versions and compare them in the browser, side by side, in this mode (in either WYSIWYG or Wiki Markup). This would make viewing changes far easier and in a much more user friendly format. The changes would still need to be highlighted.

It would fantastic if we could extend this to versioned attachments as well.

